WEBVTT

00:00:21.340 --> 00:00:22.750
It's over.

00:00:42.670 --> 00:00:43.570
What's wrong?

00:00:46.550 --> 00:00:47.580
You look decent

00:00:48.550 --> 00:00:49.610
dressed like this.

00:00:52.570 --> 00:00:53.940
Since we were little,

00:00:54.920 --> 00:00:56.920
I've known your preferences best.

00:00:59.950 --> 00:01:00.880
Do you remember?

00:01:01.550 --> 00:01:02.410
In high school,

00:01:04.310 --> 00:01:06.310
you said you liked metal models,

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:08.880
so I asked my dad to bring back

00:01:09.860 --> 00:01:11.860
limited edition models from abroad

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:14.810
just for you.

00:01:17.960 --> 00:01:19.410
As long as you like it,

00:01:20.270 --> 00:01:22.000
I'll find a way to get it for you,

00:01:23.420 --> 00:01:24.270
or...

00:01:26.650 --> 00:01:27.310
turn myself

00:01:28.130 --> 00:01:29.330
into what you like.

00:01:32.630 --> 00:01:36.360
This is the first time you've been
with the same partner for so long.

00:01:37.250 --> 00:01:38.400
Is he an exception?

00:01:42.370 --> 00:01:43.700
Exception?

00:01:45.820 --> 00:01:47.450
Rather than an exception,

00:01:49.690 --> 00:01:51.550
I just like everything about him.

00:01:54.039 --> 00:01:55.440
He's pure,

00:01:56.060 --> 00:01:57.009
yet quirky;

00:01:57.880 --> 00:01:59.210
honest,

00:02:00.520 --> 00:02:02.100
yet so stubborn.

00:02:05.350 --> 00:02:07.200
Why I like him...

00:02:08.880 --> 00:02:10.410
I just like him.

00:02:12.660 --> 00:02:14.060
There's no other reason.

00:02:20.770 --> 00:02:21.890
Alright then,

00:02:24.210 --> 00:02:25.060
since

00:02:25.190 --> 00:02:26.570
you're so sure.

00:02:29.370 --> 00:02:30.300
Have a good rest.

00:02:31.640 --> 00:02:33.110
I'll come again.

00:02:33.329 --> 00:02:33.810
OK.

00:02:33.810 --> 00:02:34.579
See you.

00:02:58.710 --> 00:02:59.460
Bye, Minwoo.

00:03:03.970 --> 00:03:04.750
Did your

00:03:05.470 --> 00:03:06.530
treatment go well?

00:03:07.220 --> 00:03:07.710
Yeah,

00:03:08.220 --> 00:03:08.970
it went well.

00:03:10.530 --> 00:03:11.430
Then,

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:14.420
there's something I want to draw.

00:03:14.910 --> 00:03:16.110
Would you be my model?

00:03:18.550 --> 00:03:19.570
Um...

00:03:19.950 --> 00:03:20.750
Give me a kiss.

00:03:24.070 --> 00:03:24.740
Approved!

00:03:24.820 --> 00:03:25.350
Let's go.

00:03:26.380 --> 00:03:26.980
Your hand.

00:03:44.470 --> 00:03:45.600
Dear master artist,

00:03:45.820 --> 00:03:47.240
can I move now?

00:03:47.350 --> 00:03:48.260
I'm tired.

00:03:48.710 --> 00:03:49.530
Wait.

00:03:50.220 --> 00:03:51.320
Just a bit longer.

00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:55.130
Whining when you can endure it.

00:04:03.660 --> 00:04:04.620
I'm done.

00:04:05.770 --> 00:04:06.450
Done?

00:04:06.450 --> 00:04:07.000
Yeah.

00:04:08.820 --> 00:04:10.080
Have a look if you want.

00:04:11.690 --> 00:04:12.410
Shall I?

00:04:12.820 --> 00:04:13.570
Sure.

00:04:14.320 --> 00:04:15.250
So impatient.

00:04:19.940 --> 00:04:20.589
Ta-da.

00:04:24.110 --> 00:04:24.860
Is this...

00:04:25.970 --> 00:04:26.520
me?

00:04:29.930 --> 00:04:31.180
That's you in my eyes.

00:04:32.270 --> 00:04:34.520
You may think it isn't accurate,

00:04:35.290 --> 00:04:37.090
but this is how you are in my eyes.

00:04:39.159 --> 00:04:40.030
No.

00:04:41.310 --> 00:04:42.370
It's too accurate.

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:45.500
It's like

00:04:46.810 --> 00:04:48.590
you see the real me.

00:04:55.260 --> 00:04:56.210
What are you doing?

00:04:56.210 --> 00:04:57.670
Wait, let me give it a try.

00:05:11.020 --> 00:05:12.810
Gosh, you're so bad at drawing.

00:05:13.020 --> 00:05:14.990
Of course. I'm not an art major.

00:05:15.640 --> 00:05:16.320
But now,

00:05:16.550 --> 00:05:18.950
with my strokes,
the drawing belongs to me.

00:05:29.340 --> 00:05:30.090
Nope.

00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:08.210
Wow.

00:06:08.210 --> 00:06:09.140
Has the sun risen from

00:06:09.140 --> 00:06:09.690
the west?

00:06:09.930 --> 00:06:11.390
You actually asked me out.

00:06:27.080 --> 00:06:28.880
I don't feel like myself lately.

00:06:30.850 --> 00:06:32.850
I want to drag him into my world,

00:06:34.240 --> 00:06:35.900
but it's not as easy this time.

00:06:37.970 --> 00:06:39.970
It was easy to control him before.

00:06:41.080 --> 00:06:42.600
Put shackles on him,

00:06:42.850 --> 00:06:44.150
be cruel,

00:06:44.500 --> 00:06:45.430
and get violent.

00:06:46.720 --> 00:06:48.320
But this is not

00:06:49.030 --> 00:06:50.110
the method I want.

00:06:51.980 --> 00:06:53.850
Being treated like this,
anyone would yield.

00:06:53.850 --> 00:06:54.780
Don't you think?

00:06:55.220 --> 00:06:55.800
Yeah.

00:06:58.710 --> 00:07:01.310
But he's been trying to
outmaneuver me lately.

00:07:02.170 --> 00:07:03.830
He doesn't listen to me at all.

00:07:08.950 --> 00:07:10.050
Isn't that good?

00:07:11.220 --> 00:07:12.690
Just tie him to you.

00:07:16.970 --> 00:07:18.820
That'd be convenient.

00:07:20.730 --> 00:07:22.730
But it's not what I want.

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:25.340
What I want is...

00:07:26.660 --> 00:07:27.590
communication.

00:07:28.690 --> 00:07:30.290
I guess it's communication.

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:35.270
Not shackles, abuse, and cruelty,

00:07:37.280 --> 00:07:39.280
but sincerity that comes from here.

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:41.930
I bet you don't understand.

00:07:42.060 --> 00:07:43.010
Wow.

00:07:44.270 --> 00:07:46.200
You even did some soul-searching?

00:07:47.270 --> 00:07:48.730
This is really unlike you.

00:07:49.860 --> 00:07:50.710
You said

00:07:51.670 --> 00:07:53.670
he's Kim Haejun,

00:07:53.980 --> 00:07:55.550
right?

00:08:02.670 --> 00:08:04.240
Don't worry.

00:08:04.610 --> 00:08:06.070
I won't do anything to him.

00:08:07.780 --> 00:08:08.780
But

00:08:09.320 --> 00:08:10.020
sometimes,

00:08:10.700 --> 00:08:12.500
I have other choices too.

00:08:54.680 --> 00:08:57.230
You've gotten much better these days.

00:08:58.630 --> 00:08:59.960
Continue the treatment

00:09:00.360 --> 00:09:01.620
and you'll get better.

00:09:09.590 --> 00:09:10.610
What is this?

00:09:12.080 --> 00:09:12.680
Here too.

00:09:21.540 --> 00:09:22.600
What are you doing?

00:09:26.910 --> 00:09:27.610
Hey.

00:09:30.500 --> 00:09:32.030
What happened to your neck?

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:39.770
I did it on purpose.

00:09:41.260 --> 00:09:42.510
To understand you,

00:09:43.530 --> 00:09:45.530
I had to do this.

00:09:52.460 --> 00:09:53.530
Are you crazy?

00:09:54.900 --> 00:09:56.900
Why did you do all that for me?

00:09:58.540 --> 00:10:01.390
Do you think this is a joke?
This is just my preference.

00:10:01.390 --> 00:10:02.450
Do you understand?

00:10:03.730 --> 00:10:05.730
You don't even know anything.

00:10:07.060 --> 00:10:09.060
Of course I had to.

00:10:13.080 --> 00:10:15.080
If I want to help you,

00:10:16.110 --> 00:10:17.390
to cure you,

00:10:18.700 --> 00:10:20.700
I need to truly know you first.

00:10:23.010 --> 00:10:23.890
Jaehun.

00:10:25.130 --> 00:10:27.020
I know you better than anyone.

00:10:29.030 --> 00:10:30.080
So,

00:10:31.610 --> 00:10:33.130
can't you choose me?

00:10:37.590 --> 00:10:39.590
I'm not afraid of you,

00:10:41.810 --> 00:10:43.130
nor will I leave you.

00:10:45.760 --> 00:10:47.310
I'll do anything

00:10:47.630 --> 00:10:49.330
you want me to.

00:10:51.720 --> 00:10:53.380
Instead of being with someone

00:10:54.060 --> 00:10:55.790
who makes you walk on eggshells

00:10:55.800 --> 00:10:57.460
and who may leave you anytime,

00:10:59.020 --> 00:11:00.620
isn't it easier to be with me?

00:11:09.530 --> 00:11:12.160
Yo, Santa's here again!

00:11:26.150 --> 00:11:27.020
Hey, Minwoo.

00:11:29.690 --> 00:11:30.740
Minwoo!

00:11:33.020 --> 00:11:35.020
You're mistaken.

00:11:37.280 --> 00:11:39.280
There's nothing between you and me.

00:11:41.800 --> 00:11:43.000
Don't cross the line.

00:12:09.410 --> 00:12:11.710
Yo, Santa's here again!

00:12:13.810 --> 00:12:14.410
Hmm?

00:12:14.410 --> 00:12:15.340
Where's Jaehun?

00:12:16.200 --> 00:12:18.530
He's getting physical therapy upstairs.

00:12:19.580 --> 00:12:20.180
Therapy?

00:12:24.950 --> 00:12:26.210
Has it been effective?

00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:29.370
Yeah,

00:12:29.370 --> 00:12:30.290
I think so.

00:12:31.240 --> 00:12:32.940
He says he's better,

00:12:33.400 --> 00:12:35.330
and Minwoo is quite professional.

00:12:36.010 --> 00:12:36.930
That's good.

00:12:38.120 --> 00:12:38.890
Let's go in.

00:12:41.240 --> 00:12:42.770
This is wine I treasure too.

00:12:43.730 --> 00:12:44.950
Another bottle?

00:12:44.950 --> 00:12:46.620
Yeah, I'm rich, remember?

00:12:48.740 --> 00:12:49.920
Wow.

00:12:51.640 --> 00:12:53.640
Jaehun is so nice to you.

00:12:56.900 --> 00:12:58.540
I drew these recently.

00:13:03.610 --> 00:13:05.470
The colors are all over the place.

00:13:06.350 --> 00:13:07.880
The composition is decent,

00:13:08.220 --> 00:13:10.810
but you didn't establish
a clear light source.

00:13:10.810 --> 00:13:13.340
You need to figure out
the overall flow first.

00:13:16.110 --> 00:13:17.990
Your talent is not outstanding,

00:13:18.750 --> 00:13:20.350
but you have artistic sense.

00:13:20.640 --> 00:13:21.440
The problem is

00:13:21.920 --> 00:13:23.200
your weak foundation.

00:13:23.310 --> 00:13:25.910
When you have many ideas,
you tend to go astray.

00:13:26.080 --> 00:13:26.770
Or you could

00:13:27.040 --> 00:13:28.320
just stay an amateur.

00:13:29.550 --> 00:13:31.680
You're going to graduate soon, right?

00:13:31.780 --> 00:13:33.340
This doesn't look good.

00:13:35.080 --> 00:13:36.630
That's why I'm worried.

00:13:37.580 --> 00:13:39.840
The professor said I need more practice.

00:13:42.130 --> 00:13:43.280
How about this?

00:13:44.010 --> 00:13:45.870
I'll come to tutor you every week.

00:13:46.560 --> 00:13:47.440
For free.

00:13:48.050 --> 00:13:49.780
Since Jaehun and I are friends.

00:13:51.020 --> 00:13:52.370
Do you know how to draw?

00:13:55.430 --> 00:13:56.880
You really don't know me.

00:13:57.610 --> 00:13:59.010
I'm a Fine Arts graduate.

00:13:59.120 --> 00:14:01.380
A graduation project is
a piece of cake to me.

00:14:01.380 --> 00:14:02.060
Oh,

00:14:02.210 --> 00:14:03.210
Yoon Minwoo!

00:14:05.050 --> 00:14:06.400
Why are you here?

00:14:08.750 --> 00:14:09.650
Soohyung is

00:14:09.880 --> 00:14:11.160
really professional.

00:14:12.520 --> 00:14:13.770
I think

00:14:13.900 --> 00:14:15.380
he'll be of help to me.

00:14:17.920 --> 00:14:19.380
If you think so, then sure.

00:14:20.030 --> 00:14:21.490
Hey, manage the time well.

00:14:22.020 --> 00:14:23.680
Don't get in Kim Haejun's way.

00:14:24.170 --> 00:14:25.450
Of course.

00:14:27.170 --> 00:14:28.370
Let's go, Yoon Minwoo.

00:14:28.370 --> 00:14:29.430
I'll take you home.

00:15:03.290 --> 00:15:05.070
Instead of being with someone

00:15:05.530 --> 00:15:07.260
who makes you walk on eggshells

00:15:07.310 --> 00:15:08.970
and who may leave you anytime,

00:15:09.290 --> 00:15:10.890
isn't it easier to be with me?

00:15:20.160 --> 00:15:21.030
Jaehun-hyung.

00:15:21.560 --> 00:15:23.090
Something's bothering me.

00:15:30.460 --> 00:15:31.240
Haejun.

00:15:33.120 --> 00:15:33.820
Come here.

00:15:45.410 --> 00:15:46.260
Kneel.

00:15:58.150 --> 00:15:59.010
Jaehun-hyung.

00:16:06.180 --> 00:16:08.350
Our relationship is contractual.

00:16:12.330 --> 00:16:13.670
Without the contract,

00:16:17.120 --> 00:16:18.580
would you still choose me?

00:16:22.970 --> 00:16:23.770
Stop.

00:16:28.330 --> 00:16:29.350
Tie your hands

00:16:31.150 --> 00:16:32.180
and look at me.

00:17:10.510 --> 00:17:11.240
I knew it.

00:17:14.010 --> 00:17:15.869
This is the most comfortable way.

00:18:10.470 --> 00:18:11.870
Already feeling it?

00:18:13.190 --> 00:18:15.190
I haven't even started.

00:18:27.030 --> 00:18:27.860
I...

00:18:29.390 --> 00:18:30.440
can prove it.

00:20:01.150 --> 00:20:03.710
You've gotten much better these days.

00:20:05.020 --> 00:20:06.350
Continue the treatment

00:20:06.780 --> 00:20:08.040
and you'll get better.

00:20:17.810 --> 00:20:18.780
What now?

00:20:20.350 --> 00:20:21.250
Nothing.

00:20:23.130 --> 00:20:24.350
I just...

00:20:25.850 --> 00:20:27.850
like it when we're alone.

00:20:32.380 --> 00:20:34.110
There's only the two of us here.

00:20:35.860 --> 00:20:37.460
You can do whatever you want.

00:20:39.290 --> 00:20:41.450
And I'll do whatever you want.

00:20:44.190 --> 00:20:46.450
I know you're thinking about Kim Haejun.

00:20:47.840 --> 00:20:48.720
But...

00:20:49.880 --> 00:20:51.180
I can

00:20:51.550 --> 00:20:53.150
satisfy you better than him.

00:20:54.540 --> 00:20:55.560
Then continue.

00:20:56.020 --> 00:20:56.590
Try it.

00:20:59.500 --> 00:21:00.780
Go on!

00:21:00.780 --> 00:21:03.040
I know you're thinking about Kim Haejun!

00:21:04.240 --> 00:21:05.040
But...

00:21:07.040 --> 00:21:08.820
I can

00:21:10.340 --> 00:21:12.570
satisfy you better than him.

00:21:14.980 --> 00:21:15.650
How?

00:21:16.250 --> 00:21:17.520
What do you even know?

00:21:17.990 --> 00:21:19.920
You think you know
about me and Kim Haejun?

00:21:19.920 --> 00:21:21.920
Answer me then!

00:21:22.420 --> 00:21:23.350
What do you know?

00:21:23.920 --> 00:21:25.050
Tell me!

00:21:25.110 --> 00:21:26.480
I can do better than him!

00:21:26.910 --> 00:21:28.230
What can you do?

00:21:28.230 --> 00:21:29.120
Do it then!

00:21:29.180 --> 00:21:30.240
You can't, can you?

00:21:32.100 --> 00:21:33.660
Please give me a chance.

00:21:35.000 --> 00:21:36.000
Please!

00:21:38.650 --> 00:21:39.150
Hey.

00:21:40.510 --> 00:21:41.430
A chance?

00:21:43.790 --> 00:21:45.990
Chances are earned, not given!

00:21:46.670 --> 00:21:49.270
Must I give you a chance
because we're friends?

00:21:50.470 --> 00:21:51.470
Get lost.

00:21:52.300 --> 00:21:53.630
Don't ever come back.

00:22:27.160 --> 00:22:28.160
Minwoo.

00:22:28.860 --> 00:22:30.160
It's over already?

00:22:32.950 --> 00:22:33.900
Let's

00:22:34.320 --> 00:22:35.420
eat together.

00:22:38.560 --> 00:22:39.310
No.

00:22:40.190 --> 00:22:42.850
He doesn't like eating
at someone else's house.

00:22:44.960 --> 00:22:46.620
I'm craving pizza.

00:22:47.270 --> 00:22:48.840
Can you buy me pizza?

00:22:57.730 --> 00:22:58.530
I'll go buy it.

00:23:10.020 --> 00:23:10.920
Minwoo.

00:23:12.150 --> 00:23:14.150
If you're free,

00:23:14.690 --> 00:23:16.110
can we talk?

00:23:38.770 --> 00:23:39.970
Have you known Jaehun

00:23:40.560 --> 00:23:42.190
for a long time?

00:23:44.500 --> 00:23:45.250
Jaehun and I?

00:23:47.420 --> 00:23:49.620
We were close since elementary school.

00:23:50.400 --> 00:23:51.860
Including Kang Soohyung.

00:23:52.580 --> 00:23:53.810
The three of us were

00:23:54.170 --> 00:23:56.170
inseparable.

00:23:59.510 --> 00:24:01.510
He seldom tells me about his past.

00:24:03.840 --> 00:24:05.500
That's how he's like.

00:24:06.690 --> 00:24:08.550
How long have you been seeing him?

00:24:09.620 --> 00:24:10.620
About half a year.

00:24:11.700 --> 00:24:13.070
Half a year?

00:24:15.440 --> 00:24:16.470
Jaehun...

00:24:18.070 --> 00:24:19.050
In the past,

00:24:19.270 --> 00:24:21.270
he's slept with all sorts of people.

00:24:22.760 --> 00:24:23.630
But

00:24:25.610 --> 00:24:28.210
I guess he's into
the college student type now.

00:24:29.780 --> 00:24:31.310
His taste has changed a lot.

00:24:34.940 --> 00:24:36.200
With love, I think that

00:24:37.350 --> 00:24:40.680
rather than the length of relationship
or personal tastes,

00:24:40.730 --> 00:24:42.390
feelings are more important.

00:24:44.160 --> 00:24:46.160
I think Jaehun thinks so too.

00:24:48.050 --> 00:24:49.520
Jaehun and I are together

00:24:50.690 --> 00:24:52.260
because we need each other.

00:24:56.250 --> 00:24:57.070
Sure.

00:24:57.380 --> 00:24:58.180
Of course.

00:24:59.160 --> 00:25:00.210
But

00:25:00.780 --> 00:25:01.780
in our community,

00:25:02.740 --> 00:25:04.940
many things matter more than feelings.

00:25:05.520 --> 00:25:06.290
Identity,

00:25:06.840 --> 00:25:07.620
status,

00:25:08.360 --> 00:25:09.890
and sexual compatibility.

00:25:12.370 --> 00:25:14.370
Especially for people like Jaehun.

00:25:14.860 --> 00:25:15.740
What he wants

00:25:16.680 --> 00:25:18.340
is more than just a companion.

00:25:19.980 --> 00:25:20.980
He needs someone

00:25:21.480 --> 00:25:23.410
who understands his entire world,

00:25:26.040 --> 00:25:27.370
including the darkness

00:25:27.500 --> 00:25:28.250
in his heart.

00:25:30.380 --> 00:25:31.260
Haejun.

00:25:32.330 --> 00:25:33.380
You're too young.

00:25:34.760 --> 00:25:36.420
You might not be able to handle

00:25:37.440 --> 00:25:38.640
someone like Jaehun.

00:25:40.370 --> 00:25:41.230
In other words,

00:25:42.470 --> 00:25:44.470
he's not suitable for you.

00:25:53.460 --> 00:25:54.390
I...

00:25:57.030 --> 00:25:58.730
trust his choice.

00:26:00.480 --> 00:26:02.810
I'll also be responsible for this choice.

00:26:04.750 --> 00:26:05.400
Alright.

00:26:06.410 --> 00:26:07.280
Good luck then.

00:26:24.270 --> 00:26:26.270
Haejun, I bought pizza!

00:26:30.510 --> 00:26:31.440
What's going on?

00:26:32.400 --> 00:26:34.090
Why are you still here?

00:26:35.260 --> 00:26:36.060
I just

00:26:36.900 --> 00:26:38.630
talked about the past with him.

00:26:41.200 --> 00:26:42.150
Let me do it.

00:26:46.070 --> 00:26:47.500
Are you leaving?

00:26:48.790 --> 00:26:49.320
I should.

00:26:49.430 --> 00:26:50.100
It's late.

00:26:50.990 --> 00:26:53.050
I can't spend the night at your place.

00:27:02.960 --> 00:27:04.240
Coming.

00:27:07.000 --> 00:27:09.000
Hey, hello!

00:27:11.040 --> 00:27:12.370
Yoon Minwoo is here too.

00:27:13.980 --> 00:27:15.780
Soohyung, what brings you here?

00:27:16.750 --> 00:27:18.540
That's what I want to know to.

00:27:18.920 --> 00:27:19.970
Why are you here?

00:27:20.500 --> 00:27:22.810
There was some wine left at home.

00:27:22.980 --> 00:27:24.780
Isn't it nice to drink together?

00:27:27.660 --> 00:27:28.290
Hey.

00:27:28.930 --> 00:27:30.650
It's not easy for us to get together.

00:27:30.650 --> 00:27:31.580
How about a game?

00:27:31.940 --> 00:27:32.740
A game?

00:27:33.960 --> 00:27:35.690
What do you think, Yoon Minwoo?

00:27:35.980 --> 00:27:36.710
Sounds good.

00:27:43.900 --> 00:27:45.070
Truth or Dare.

00:27:46.230 --> 00:27:46.980
OK?

00:28:01.080 --> 00:28:03.080
Let's have a drink before we start.

00:28:04.690 --> 00:28:05.690
Why the long face?

00:28:06.800 --> 00:28:07.910
Don't be a killjoy.

00:28:08.150 --> 00:28:08.920
Hurry up.

00:28:10.530 --> 00:28:11.000
Come on.

00:28:11.130 --> 00:28:11.930
Cheers!

00:28:15.000 --> 00:28:15.980
Can I drink?

00:28:18.360 --> 00:28:19.110
Yes, you can.

00:28:24.740 --> 00:28:26.840
I'll get the ball rolling.

00:28:38.560 --> 00:28:39.310
Soohyung.

00:28:40.350 --> 00:28:42.350
Go ahead.

00:28:42.840 --> 00:28:44.840
I have many secrets.

00:28:47.810 --> 00:28:48.660
How many

00:28:49.730 --> 00:28:50.990
people have you dated?

00:28:56.180 --> 00:28:56.970
Zero.

00:28:58.350 --> 00:29:00.280
Have you been single all your life?

00:29:00.550 --> 00:29:01.380
Well,

00:29:01.470 --> 00:29:03.470
dating doesn't have to be involved.

00:29:04.260 --> 00:29:07.260
He's probably slept with
more people than Jaehun has.

00:29:10.510 --> 00:29:11.380
Then...

00:29:13.320 --> 00:29:14.620
are you a top?

00:29:15.870 --> 00:29:17.280
If you're curious,

00:29:18.080 --> 00:29:19.490
let's give it a go.

00:29:20.460 --> 00:29:22.120
Are you drunk, Kang Soohyung?

00:29:24.110 --> 00:29:26.190
You're drunk. That's enough.

00:29:29.750 --> 00:29:31.060
Fine.

00:29:47.970 --> 00:29:48.720
OK.

00:29:49.280 --> 00:29:51.280
Since it was me, I'll spin it again.

00:29:58.450 --> 00:29:59.200
Me?

00:30:00.850 --> 00:30:02.250
I really have no secrets.

00:30:07.160 --> 00:30:09.090
What if you don't get what you want?

00:30:11.920 --> 00:30:13.320
I'll do whatever it takes

00:30:15.480 --> 00:30:17.100
until I get it.

00:30:18.040 --> 00:30:20.100
What if you destroy it in the process?

00:30:20.590 --> 00:30:21.920
Even if it's destroyed,

00:30:23.650 --> 00:30:25.110
what's mine is still mine.

00:30:34.980 --> 00:30:35.930
OK, who's next?

00:30:38.320 --> 00:30:39.250
Let's stop here.

00:30:39.270 --> 00:30:40.260
It's boring.

00:30:41.790 --> 00:30:42.820
Go home, you two.

00:30:43.190 --> 00:30:44.670
We've played enough.

00:30:46.960 --> 00:30:48.480
You should go back.

00:30:54.270 --> 00:30:54.950
Let's go.

00:30:56.780 --> 00:30:57.830
Let's go.

00:31:27.730 --> 00:31:28.230
Jaehun.

00:31:30.170 --> 00:31:31.900
How many people have you dated?

00:31:53.170 --> 00:31:54.570
I've never dated anyone.

00:31:57.240 --> 00:31:59.240
It was always contractual.

00:32:00.300 --> 00:32:02.630
I've never been in a proper relationship.

00:32:06.230 --> 00:32:09.160
Is there really nothing
between you and Yoon Minwoo?

00:32:11.280 --> 00:32:12.830
I saw pictures of you two

00:32:14.440 --> 00:32:15.470
on the canvas.

00:32:18.250 --> 00:32:19.790
He seems to like you.

00:32:21.860 --> 00:32:23.490
You seem to like him too.

00:32:25.420 --> 00:32:26.300
Me?

00:32:29.230 --> 00:32:30.450
Minwoo and I...

00:32:32.430 --> 00:32:34.560
I can't believe I have to explain this,

00:32:35.490 --> 00:32:37.090
but there's really nothing.

00:32:39.720 --> 00:32:41.180
Don't change the subject.

00:32:43.740 --> 00:32:44.200
Haejun.

00:32:45.700 --> 00:32:47.070
Minwoo, Soohyung, and I

00:32:48.170 --> 00:32:50.500
have been best friends since we were kids.

00:32:51.620 --> 00:32:53.820
We know each other well,
so we know how to

00:32:54.280 --> 00:32:56.830
treat each other
and make each other happy.

00:32:58.770 --> 00:33:00.780
There's never been anything romantic.

00:33:00.780 --> 00:33:02.210
I swear.

00:33:02.870 --> 00:33:04.200
Have you slept with him?

00:33:07.060 --> 00:33:07.700
Hey.

00:33:08.540 --> 00:33:10.370
Who do you think I am?

00:33:10.730 --> 00:33:12.730
Why'd I sleep with my buddy?

00:33:16.030 --> 00:33:18.360
But Minwoo doesn't seem to think that way.

00:33:22.920 --> 00:33:23.700
Kim Haejun.

00:33:24.650 --> 00:33:27.180
Is that why you've been
coming on to me lately?

00:33:27.830 --> 00:33:29.630
Because you see them as threats?

00:33:31.500 --> 00:33:32.850
That's not what I mean.

00:33:46.310 --> 00:33:48.440
It seems like I've come all this way...

00:33:53.000 --> 00:33:54.250
just to

00:33:56.030 --> 00:33:57.480
get to you.

00:34:02.500 --> 00:34:03.760
I've finally arrived.

00:34:55.780 --> 00:34:56.520
Now,

00:34:58.580 --> 00:35:00.710
I want to accept everything about you.

00:35:57.240 --> 00:36:10.360
[Tide of Love 2]

00:37:29.920 --> 00:37:38.400
[Tide of Love 2]